dct_title_s: Inyo County, California, GIS Maps and Data
dct_description_sm: This collection contains shapefiles downloaded from the Inyo County California GIS Maps and Data Collection (https://www.inyocounty.us/gis/GISPage_Data.htm).
System requirements: Geographic Information Systems (GIS) software that reads ESRI shapefile format.
